{"tid":1224064,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊起底？] 透過612指揮官，學下外國名","createTime":"2019-06-15T01:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T01:51:40.000Z","uid":135287,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1dfdb4cf335f84ddc8924a7f322840c34c7c41","tid":1224064,"uid":135287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:47:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190613/59711209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711209&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=42053cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711209&h=b941dd0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190613/59711209</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;新界南總區應變大隊主力負責守衛添華道立法會大樓方向防線，由該區指揮官外籍總警司陶輝&quot;<br />\n<br />\n陶輝英文名係 Rupert Dover<br />\n不過呢，外國人全名，就通常仲有Middle Name，通常係繼承自早代嘅名。<br />\n陶輝全名係 Rupert Timothy Alan Dover<br />\n佢攞過咩獎，就上面link 睇啦<br />\n<br />\n&quot;至於「速龍小隊」則由警察機動部隊校長外籍總警司莊定賢&quot;<br />\n<br />\n莊定賢，全名係David John Jordan, 好似係英國人黎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 學術看名字<br />\n起底還起底，但都不忘民意戰<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享</span></span>"},{"pid":"b6858caef4fc4c4bccbee044cb5bc6a534304a13","tid":1224064,"uid":244303,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"佢叫咩名關我尻事咩<br />\n我淨係知呢兩條閪鬼佬叫啲警犬打尻我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}